{BasicAreaChart}
{AreaSpalineChart}
{BarChart}
{ColumnChart}
{BubbleChart}
{SteplineChart}
{ColumnChart}
{PieChart}
{DonutChart}
{MixedChart}
{CandlestickChart}

); } export default Apexcharts;
